snippet.title: William DEFENDS STAFF/Meghan/Michelle Obama SUBVERT/SHAFTING Dad/PRINCESS's DEAFNESS/CON ARTIST
snippet.description:
Please sign Lady Colin Campbell's Petition inviting Prince Harry to ask The Queen to put his titles & royal status into abeyance. https://www.change.org/p/the-public-invitation-to-prince-harry-to-request-the-queen-to-put-his-titles-into-abeyance?utm_content=cl_sharecopy_28949031_en-GB%3A8&recruiter=1205195839&utm_source=share_petition&utm_medium=copylink&utm_campaign=share_petition

🇬🇧 Book order https://www.amazon.co.uk/Meghan-Harry-Lady-Colin-Campbell/dp/1916131719
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Queens-Marriage-Lady-Colin-Campbell/dp/1527209849
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/People-Colour-Royals-Colin-Campbell/dp/1916131700
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Real-Diana-Colin-Lady-Campbell/dp/1900850958
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Diana-Private-Princess-Nobody-Knows/dp/0312081804
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Untold-Life-Queen-Elizabeth-Mother/dp/0956803814
                          https://www.amazon.co.uk/Daughter-Narcissus-Struggle-Narcissistic-Personality/dp/0992816181

In the hundred and sixty-fith episode Lady Colin Campbell addresses the issue of Meghan and Michelle Obama using their influence to comfort Naomi Osaka and the unwelcome effect of subverting the press; agrees that a positive consequence  of the Markle Debacle has been the education people have gained in personality disorders and mental illness as a direct consequence of the ongoing saga; examines the state of Prince Albert and Princess Charlene of Monaco's marriage and confirms that she is in danger of losing her hearing if she travels; discusses Angela Gulbenkian being found guilty of fraud, facing prison time, and explains why being Duarte Gulbenkian's wife does not give her access to the wealth of the Gulbenkian Foundation; answers a question on Meghan's massive dossier on the bullying charges; why the Treason Act of 1884 won't be used against Meghan and Harry even though they would have been lost their heads in earlier centuries; explains how Meghan and Harry's PR teams and their tame publications profit no matter how popular or unpopular the couples is; explains why Harry and Meghan are expoitable despite having the wrong age demographic; agrees that Prince William showed courage in defending his staff against the bullying claims against his sister-in-law; and answers the question of why she and The Queen wear brooches on the left side.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/LadyColinCampb?re...​
